<div class="riskr-press">

  <div class="riskr-press__hero page-width">
    <p class="riskr-press__eyebrow">Press &amp; Coverage</p>
    <h1 class="riskr-press__headline">
      As seen in prestigious publications.
    </h1>
    <p class="riskr-press__subhead">
      Leading voices in corporate innovation, apparel disruption, and synergy materialization have taken notice.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="riskr-press__divider"></div>

  <div class="riskr-press__quotes page-width">

    <div class="riskr-press__quote">
      <p class="riskr-press__quote-text">"Riskr has successfully identified an underserved market at the intersection of business casual and existential dread."</p>
      <p class="riskr-press__quote-source">Forbes, probably</p>
    </div>

    <div class="riskr-press__quote">
      <p class="riskr-press__quote-text">"These shirts communicate more about your strategic alignment than any deck you've ever presented."</p>
      <p class="riskr-press__quote-source">Harvard Business Review (unconfirmed)</p>
    </div>

    <div class="riskr-press__quote">
      <p class="riskr-press__quote-text">"We named Riskr one of the Top 10 Disruptors in Wearable Corporate Communication for the third consecutive quarter."</p>
      <p class="riskr-press__quote-source">A Newsletter We Started</p>
    </div>

    <div class="riskr-press__quote">
      <p class="riskr-press__quote-text">"Finally, an apparel brand that understands our pain. And our OKRs."</p>
      <p class="riskr-press__quote-source">r/LinkedInLunatics</p>
    </div>

    <div class="riskr-press__quote">
      <p class="riskr-press__quote-text">"I wore a Riskr shirt to my Series A pitch meeting. We closed the round. Coincidence? Our analysts say no."</p>
      <p class="riskr-press__quote-source">Anonymous Founder (probably not a founder)</p>
    </div>

    <div class="riskr-press__quote">
      <p class="riskr-press__quote-text">"Disrupting disruption itself. Riskr is the first post-ironic clothing brand for the post-ironic professional."</p>
      <p class="riskr-press__quote-source">TechCrunch (we wish)</p>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="riskr-press__divider"></div>

  <div class="riskr-press__contact page-width">
    <div class="riskr-press__contact-label">
      <span class="riskr-press__label">Media Inquiries</span>
    </div>
    <div class="riskr-press__contact-body">
      <p>For press inquiries, partnership opportunities, or requests to have your quote fabricated and displayed on this page, please contact our Communications &amp; Narrative Engineering department.</p>
      <p>We respond to all inquiries within 3–5 business days, pending synergy availability.</p>
      <a href="mailto:press@riskr.inc" class="riskr-press__contact-link">
        press@riskr.inc <span class="riskr-press__link-arrow">&rarr;</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>

<style>
  .riskr-press {
    background: #fff;
  }

  .riskr-press__hero {
    padding-block: 100px 80px;
  }

  .riskr-press__eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-body--family);
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.38);
    margin: 0 0 28px;
  }

  .riskr-press__headline {
    font-family: var(--font-heading--family);
    font-size: clamp(32px, 5.5vw, 72px);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 0.95;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    color: #000;
    margin: 0 0 28px;
  }

  .riskr-press__subhead {
    font-family: var(--font-body--family);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.52);
    max-width: 520px;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .riskr-press__divider {
    border-top: 1px solid #e8e8e8;
  }

  .riskr-press__quotes {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 0;
    padding-block: 0;
  }

  .riskr-press__quote {
    padding: 56px 48px 56px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e8e8e8;
  }

  .riskr-press__quote:nth-child(even) {
    padding-left: 48px;
    padding-right: 0;
    border-left: 1px solid #e8e8e8;
  }

  .riskr-press__quote-text {
    font-family: var(--font-heading--family);
    font-size: clamp(16px, 1.8vw, 22px);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.45;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    color: #000;
    margin: 0 0 20px;
  }

  .riskr-press__quote-source {
    font-family: var(--font-body--family);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.38);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .riskr-press__contact {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 200px 1fr;
    gap: 0 80px;
    padding-block: 72px;
  }

  .riskr-press__contact-label {
    padding-top: 4px;
  }

  .riskr-press__label {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-body--family);
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.38);
  }

  .riskr-press__contact-body p {
    font-family: var(--font-body--family);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65);
    max-width: 560px;
    margin: 0 0 16px;
  }

  .riskr-press__contact-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 4px;
    font-family: var(--font-body--family);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #000;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #000;
    padding-bottom: 2px;
    margin-top: 8px;
  }

  .riskr-press__link-arrow {
    display: inline-block;
    transition: transform 0.2s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
  }

  .riskr-press__contact-link:hover .riskr-press__link-arrow {
    transform: translateX(5px);
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .riskr-press__hero {
      padding-block: 72px 56px;
    }

    .riskr-press__quotes {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .riskr-press__quote {
      padding: 40px 0;
    }

    .riskr-press__quote:nth-child(even) {
      padding-left: 0;
      border-left: none;
    }

    .riskr-press__contact {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 24px;
      padding-block: 56px;
    }
  }
</style>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Riskr Press",
  "tag": "section",
  "class": "riskr-press-section",
  "settings": [],
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "Riskr Press"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
